quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  22,16,Kotero Ife talitumiza ilo ngati zizindikiro zooneka ndipo ndithudi Mulungu amatsogolera aliyense amene Iye wamufuna
  22,17,"Ndithudi iwo amene amakhulupirira, ndi iwo amene ndi Ayuda, Masabina, Akhirisitu, a Magiyani ndi akunja, ndi iwo amene amapembedza zinthu zina mowonjezera pa Mulungu. Ndithudi, Mulungu adzawaweruza pa tsiku la kuuka kwa akufa ndipo Mulungu ndi mboni pa zinthu zonse"
  22,18,"Kodi iwe siudaone kuti zinthu zonse zimalambira Mulungu mwachitsanzo zinthu zimene zimakhala kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi monga dzuwa, mwezi, nyenyezi, mapiri mitengo, nyama ndi anthu ambiri? Koma pali ambiri amene chilango ndi chowayenera. Aliyense amene achititsidwa manyazi ndi Mulungu, palibe wina amene angamulemekeze. Ndithudi! Mulungu amachita zimene afuna"
  22,19,"Awa awiri otsutsana, akutsutsana za Ambuye wawo ndipo akakhala sakhulupirira Mulungu, adzawasokera zovala za ku moto ndipo madzi ogaduka adzathiridwa paliombo pawo"
  22,20,Ndi iwo zidzasungunuka zonse zimene zili m’mimba mwawo ndi pa makungu pawo
  22,21,Iwo adzamangidwa ku unyolo wa zitsulo
  22,22,"Nthawi iliyonse imene azidzafuna kuti athawe m’menemo, chifukwa chaululu, azidzabwezedwa momwemo ndipo adzauzidwa kuti, “Lawani chilango chamoto.”"
  22,23,"Ndithudi Mulungu adzawalowetsa anthu okhulupirira ndi ochita ntchito zabwino, m’minda yothiriridwa ndi mitsinje yoyenda. Iwo adzavekedwa zibangiri za golide ndi mphete za nkhombe ndipo zovala zawo zidzakhala za silika"